headline: AI Stocks Are Taking a Beating. What to Buy Instead.
summary: November has been NO-vember when it comes to tech stocks.  Investors are shunning artificial-intelligence leaders and other momentum names.  Investors seem to be embracing drug stocks, insurers, and medical equipment companies again.

headline: Solventum inks $725M Acera takeover
summary: The company has stepped up its interest in M&A since making a $4.1 billion divestiture that strengthened its balance sheet.
